### Coins API Testing - HTTP Requests
### Use with REST Client extension in VS Code or similar tools

@baseUrl = http://localhost:4000/api
@token = YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get Coin Bundles
GET {{baseUrl}}/coins/bundles
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

